This paper is about natural language processing and machine learning techniques for relation extraction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks and deep learning techniques, which are commonly associated with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of word embeddings, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing. Finally, the paper discusses the use of joint learning, which is a technique commonly used in neural networks and reinforcement learning (cs.NE).
